- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the optimization of UAVs for coverage enhancement in a hybrid satellite-terrestrial communication network. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper deals with optimizing the transmit power of UAVs subject to constraints on interference and backhaul, which involves information theory concepts. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper involves optimizing the trajectory of UAVs subject to kinematic constraints. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve security considerations in coordinating the different communication systems. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also less likely but possible as the paper may involve using AI techniques for optimization.
